             flow will be executed sequentially on predecessors failure, until at least one capability finishes successfully, and then rest of the recovery capabilities 
             will be skipped and the main plan will continue execution.Following example plan shows how to navigate to a series of waypoints, specifically (5.0, 5.0), (2.0,2.0) and (3.0, 1.0) in order. And if the robot 
